summary:
You are an experienced sniper in the secret terrorists base. All the most dangerous criminals hide there and plot evil plans. Your mission is to destroy the base and all the criminals.

- Come to secret bases of terrorists in different locations;
- Use your modern sniper rifle for shooting;
- Aim accurately and make critical shots;
- Complete various sniper missions.

Sniper Shooter 3D - SWAT Missions game is full of dangerous missions and shootouts with criminals. 

Key features of Sniper Shooter 3D - SWAT Missions game:

- Lots of bases of criminals and terrorists;
- Only one experienced sniper;
- Powerful sniper rifle for critical shots;
- Lots of dangerous tasks and missions.
